             sys_choice_case_task_status.xml; the type=Review and
             status=Closed choice values must be registered)
        - The auto-numbering record at
            ../../numbers/sys_number_x_casemgmt_case_task.xml  (the
             platform may auto-generate a TASK0000008-format value if
