                  ServiceNow Date field format - NOT DateTime; no
                  timezone, no time-of-day component. The relative -2
                  days offset places the due_date in the recent past,
                  consistent with a recently-due-then-completed task
                  pattern. The build-time computation ensures the
                  value remains semantically meaningful regardless of
                  when the Update Set is imported.)

      Rule 4 - Reference resolution by stable human-readable key (AAP
              Section 0.7.2 "NO sys_id literals anywhere"):
